    dc:description "Figure 3. Left sagittae of Aphanius anatoliae anatoliae of south-west Anatolia (Lake District), except (k) right sagitta, mirrored. Localities: Yeşilova/Lake Salda (a–f), Doğanbaba/Lake Salda (g–j), Düğer (k–m), Lake Avlan (n–u), Işıklı dam (v, w). (a–h, k, n–r) Females; (i, j, l, m, s–w) males." ;
