<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10092228>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Left sagittae of Aphanius anatoliae anatoliae of south-west (Lake District) (a–g) and western central Anatolia (h–t), except (a) right sagitta, mirrored. Localities: Kovada Canal (a, b), Lake Eğirdir/Barla (c, d), Lake Eğirdir/Eğirdir (e–g), Eflatunpınarı/Beyşehir (h–m), İnsuyu/Cihanbeyli (n), and Akkaya/Niğde (o–t). (a, c, e, f, h–j, o–q) Females; (b, d, g, k–n, r–t) males." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10092228/files/figure.png" ;
